<p>While Ethereum has been the pioneer in terms of DeFi protocols and advancements, Bitcoin has also started to make its mark in this space.</p>



<p>As of now, Ethereum dominates the DeFi market with over $60 billion locked in various protocols, showcasing its strong position in the industry.</p>



<p>However, with Bitcoin&#8217;s potential and advancements, it&#8217;s expected to become a formidable player in the future of DeFi.</p>
